路易斯‧拉莫斯（Luis Ramos）在「拉巴斯公民」[寫到](http://citizenlapaz.blogspot.com/2010/09/ley-
antiracismo-en-bolivia-mi-opinion.html
"http://citizenlapaz.blogspot.com/2010/09/ley-antiracismo-en-bolivia-mi-
opinion.html") [西] 他對[反種族主義法案](http://achacachi.blogspot.com/2010/09/anti-
racism-law-guarantees-equality-in.html
"http://achacachi.blogspot.com/2010/09/anti-racism-law-guarantees-equality-
in.html")的想法。對於記者們[關切](http://knightcenter.utexas.edu/blog/bolivian-
journalists-criticize-anti-racism-bill
"http://knightcenter.utexas.edu/blog/bolivian-journalists-criticize-anti-
racism-bill")這項法案並抨擊此舉侵害言論自由，路易斯的回應是：「放棄種族污辱有那麼難嗎？」

